</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="189v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l1">Crıſtoff von <expan>Layming<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Crıſtoff / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l3">ſıch an dem geſloſſ ʒu lawff <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> hat etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l4"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd ıſt vns ſölıch geſchıcht niht lıeb / Als Jr vns denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l5">ſchreıbt wıe Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtanden</expan> habt / daʒ ſölıch dıe es <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan . awſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> geleyt getan <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Da ıſt vns niht wıſſend von Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l7"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> vns niht wol gemaint / wır haben <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lantman<ex>n</ex>ſweıs</expan> <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l8">daʒ ſölıch dıe das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan . in der Stat ʒu lawff geleyt gehabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l9"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Ob dem alſo ſey <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> niht <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır niht / Denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l10">eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan><ex>con</ex>u<ex>er</ex>ſıo<ex>nem</ex></expan> Paulȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="189v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Cristoff von <expan>Layming<ex>en</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Cristoff, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der sich an dem gesloss zu Lawff
                                <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> hat etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und ist uns sölich geschicht niht lieb. Als ir uns denn schreibt, wie ir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>standen</expan> habt, daz sölich, die es
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan, awsz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> geleyt getan
                            <expan>sölte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, da ist uns niht wissend von und
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> uns niht wol gemaint; wir haben
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lantman<ex>n</ex>sweis</expan>
<expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz sölich, die das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> getan, in der stat zu Lawff geleyt gehabt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, ob dem also sey
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> niht, <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        niht. Denn wo wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan><ex>con</ex>v<ex>er</ex>sio<ex>nem</ex></expan> Pauli.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
